  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Washingtonian com also collects information automatically through the use of electronic tools such as cookies and clickstream data Cookies help provide a customized web experience by enabling us to identify web users who visit our site Among other things the cookie may store your Washingtonian com user name and password You may choose not to provide such information by adjusting your Internet browser security settings to refuse cookies Doing so however may limit your ability to access certain pages available on the website and may prevent you from enjoying the features on our website enabled by cookies</evidence>
